&lt;li&gt;Mentor, support, collaborate with, and learn from other members of the team as well as other key stakeholders across the company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to an engineering culture of shipping great products. Advocate for new technologies, methods, best practices and solutions (technical and non-technical) that improve our product and work experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ship new code on a daily basis covering the following areas:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Frontend features, components, designs, and general architecture supporting everything a user needs to do on our site&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Backend services supporting the entire marketplace including interfacing with data pipelines and supporting the frontend&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;External integrations with third parties including different product information and order placement APIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Search infrastructure and optimizations for scientific use-cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
